Summary The Business Problem Borussia Dortmund is one of the top teams in German Soccer League. But in some of the past seasons they have had inconsistent performances. Our objective is to help the team stay consistent with their performance and win the German League.
Our analysis is directed to help the coach of Borussia Dortmund take strategic decisions and make sure that team becomes the champion in the next season.
